<h2 id="lyrics-and-chords">Lyrics and chords</h2>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>INTRO
  Em

VERSE
  Em                           Am            B7                      Em   (Em /D)
  ...Sitting on a highway in a broken van... thinking of you--- again
  C                                       G
