  C                              G     B7
  ...With every step I see your face

  Em                       Am            B7                          Em   (Em /D)
  ...Like a mirror looking back at me... saying you're the only one
  C                             G
  ...Making me feel I could survive
  C                     G    B7
  ...Am so glad to be alive

CHORUS
